}} (And reply by F. Wilczek.)</ref>有人説，RHIC引發末日情景的風險至少有五千萬分之一的可能性。<ref>Cf. Brookhaven National Laboratory Report mentioned by Martin Rees, Baron Rees of Ludlow|Rees, Martin (Lord), ''Our Final Century: Will the Human Race Survive the Twenty-first Century?'', U.K., 2003, {{ISBN|0-465-06862-6}}; note that the mentioned "1 in 50 million" chance is disputed as being a misleading and played down probability of the serious risks (Aspden, U.K., 2006)</ref>關于RHIC可能產生[[奇異夸克團|奇異夸克團]]，[[牛津大學|牛津大學]]物理學教授{{tsl|en|Frank Close|克洛斯}}表示，“這種情況發生的機率就像你連續3周中彩票的大獎一樣。但問題是人們相信連續3周中彩票是可能的”。<ref name="End Day"/>經過詳細的研究，科學家們認爲，第一，RHIC的重離子實驗不會危及地球；<ref>
